OL,10,FStowupland High School brought in Barry
OL,11,FSmith after a "requires improvement"   
OL,12,FOfsted rating in December.             
OL,14,FBut one parent said others were        
OL,15,Fthinking of moving their children due  
OL,16,Fto Mr Smith's appointment.             
